title: Nate DiMeo from The Memory Palace
itunes:title: Nate DiMeo from The Memory Palace
description:
Podcasts are cool and today I have the host of one of my favorite podcasts around, The Memory Palace, Nate Dimeo on the show. I knew he had a connection to punk and hardcore, but after our conversation it's WAYYYYYY deeper than I could have ever imagined. We discuss pursuing art as a career, Ebullition Records and being a full time podcaster. Listen and learn!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
